{"tid":1366630,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[人民宣言] 當人民不再懼怕警察﹐就是香港重光之時","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:28:00.000Z","uid":37656,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c044080e0250555f36547af37df21b72f2cc0ba8","tid":1366630,"uid":37656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"當人民痛苦的生活<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有被國家看見</span></span><br />\n當人民憤怒的咆哮<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有被國家聽到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當人民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不再信任政府</span></span>可以保護自己<br />\n當人民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不再依靠警察</span></span>執法維持治安<br />\n<br />\n當人民以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">文字宣揚自由公義</span></span><br />\n當人民以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">武裝保障鄰舍安全</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當人民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">戴上口罩</span></span>不是為了<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">掩飾身份</span></span><br />\n當人民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">戴上頭盔</span></span>不是為了<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">保護頭顱</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而是為了統一裝束<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">以黑衣為標記﹐以頭盔口罩相認</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">這是人民勝利的時候<br />\n這是香港重光的時候<br />\n<br />\nONE FOR ALL<br />\nALL FOR ONE</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://directoriodenoticias.files.wordpress.com/2011/03/anonymous-legion.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdirectoriodenoticias.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F03%2Fanonymous-legion.jpg&h=5ea465d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bdf9396b85c3a6e5d76bf52e91fa37c56731ccc","tid":1366630,"uid